snippet.title: Make a Good Mega Man Level 1 Remastered - Released!
snippet.description:
Download the full game here:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FbGmvOypJgDHiaSWFSCbXYA75MkUXSas/view

Alternate download link:
https://www.dropbox.com/s/iro9bafnkmbnx7v/MaGMML1%20Remastered%20V1.0.zip?dl=0

MaGMML1 Remastered is finally here! Re-experience the first game in the series, re-built on an improved engine. There's also a bunch of new content for you to discover as well, so don't go in expecting the same game as before!

Additionally, feel free to join our Discord server, or visit the website/forums for updates on upcoming MaGMML-related content:
https://discord.gg/YtHUtfd
https://magmmlcom.ipage.com
https://magmmlcom.ipage.com/forum
